casebody.data:
Darlene SCHMIDT, Petitioner
v.
Gary R. HERBERT, Governor of Utah No. 19-5971 Supreme Court of the United States. October 21, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
